*% === Punch options ============
*OpenUI *RIPunch/Punch: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 50.0 AnySetup *RIPunch
*DefaultRIPunch: None
*RIPunch None/Off: "<</Punch 0
/PunchDetails <</Type 1 /Position 0 >>
  >> setpagedevice"
*End
*RIPunch RILL/Left Landscape: "currentpagedevice /OutputType get (Finisher Main Tray) eq
{<< /OutputType (Finisher Main Tray)>> setpagedevice} {<< /OutputType (Finisher Shift Tray)>> setpagedevice}ifelse
<< /Punch 2 /PunchDetails <</Type 1 /Position 2 >>
 >> setpagedevice"
*End
*RIPunch RILP/Left Portrait: "currentpagedevice /OutputType get (Finisher Main Tray) eq
{<< /OutputType (Finisher Main Tray)>> setpagedevice} {<< /OutputType (Finisher Shift Tray)>> setpagedevice}ifelse
<< /Punch 2 /PunchDetails <</Type 1 /Position 1 >>
  >> setpagedevice"
*End
*RIPunch RITL/Top Landscape:"currentpagedevice /OutputType get (Finisher Main Tray) eq
{<< /OutputType (Finisher Main Tray)>> setpagedevice} {<< /OutputType (Finisher Shift Tray)>> setpagedevice}ifelse
<< /Punch 2 /PunchDetails <</Type 1 /Position 6 >>
>>setpagedevice"
*End
*RIPunch RITP/Top Portrait:"currentpagedevice /OutputType get (Finisher Main Tray) eq
{<< /OutputType (Finisher Main Tray)>> setpagedevice} {<< /OutputType (Finisher Shift Tray)>> setpagedevice}ifelse
<< /Punch 2 /PunchDetails <</Type 1 /Position 5 >>
>>setpagedevice"
*End
*CloseUI: *RIPunch
*MSPrintSchemaKeywordMap: JobHolePunch *RIPunch
*MSPrintSchemaKeywordMap: JobHolePunch None *RIPunch None

*% === Toner Saver options ============
*OpenUI *RITonerSaver/Toner Saver: Boolean
*OrderDependency: 50.0 AnySetup *RITonerSaver
*DefaultRITonerSaver: False
*RITonerSaver False/Off: "<< /PostRenderingEnhance
currentpagedevice /PostRenderingEnhanceDetails get
/REValue get 0 ne
/PostRenderingEnhanceDetails
 <</Type 18 /TonerSaver 0 /REValue
currentpagedevice /PostRenderingEnhanceDetails get
/REValue get >> >> setpagedevice"
*End
*RITonerSaver True/On: "<</PostRenderingEnhance true /PostRenderingEnhanceDetails
 <</Type 18 /TonerSaver 1 /REValue
currentpagedevice /PostRenderingEnhanceDetails get
/REValue get >> >> setpagedevice"
*End
*?RITonerSaver: "
save
 currentpagedevice  /PostRenderingEnhance known
 {
  currentpagedevice /PostRenderingEnhanceDetails known
  { currentpagedevice /PostRenderingEnhanceDetails get
   dup /Type get 18 eq
   {
    /TonerSaver get 0 eq
    {(False)}
    {(True)}
    ifelse
   }
   {(False)} ifelse
  }
  {(False)} ifelse
 }
 {(False)}
  ifelse
 = flush
 restore
 "
*End
*CloseUI: *RITonerSaver

*% === Edge Smoothing options ============
*OpenUI *RIEdgeSmoothing/Edge Smoothing: Boolean
*OrderDependency: 10.0 AnySetup *RIEdgeSmoothing
*DefaultRIEdgeSmoothing: False
*RIEdgeSmoothing False/Off: "<< /PostRenderingEnhance
currentpagedevice /PostRenderingEnhanceDetails get
/TonerSaver get 0 ne
/PostRenderingEnhanceDetails
 <</Type 18 /REValue 0 /TonerSaver
currentpagedevice /PostRenderingEnhanceDetails get
/TonerSaver get >> >> setpagedevice"
*End
*RIEdgeSmoothing True/On: "<</PostRenderingEnhance true /PostRenderingEnhanceDetails
 <</Type 18 /REValue 1 /TonerSaver
currentpagedevice /PostRenderingEnhanceDetails get
/TonerSaver get >> >> setpagedevice"
*End
*?RIEdgeSmoothing: "
%!PS-Adobe
save
 currentpagedevice  /PostRenderingEnhance known
 {
  currentpagedevice /PostRenderingEnhanceDetails known
  { currentpagedevice /PostRenderingEnhanceDetails get
   dup /Type get 18 eq
   {
    /REValue get 0 eq
    {(False)}
    {(True)}
    ifelse
   }
   {(False)} ifelse
  }
  {(False)} ifelse
 }
 {(False)}
  ifelse
 = flush
 restore
 "
*End
*CloseUI: *RIEdgeSmoothing

*% === Collate options ============
*OpenUI *Collate/Collate: Boolean
*OrderDependency: 50.0 AnySetup *Collate
*DefaultCollate: True
*Collate False/Off: "<</Collate false>> setpagedevice"
*Collate True/On: "<</Collate true>> setpagedevice"
*?Collate: "save
 currentpagedevice dup /Collate known
 {/Collate get {(True)}{(False)} ifelse}
 {pop (None)}
 ifelse = flush
restore"
*End
*CloseUI: *Collate

*OpenUI *RIIdiomRecognition/Idiom Recognition: Boolean
*OrderDependency: 50.0 AnySetup *RIIdiomRecognition
*DefaultRIIdiomRecognition: True
*RIIdiomRecognition False/Off: "<</IdiomRecognition false>> setuserparams"
*RIIdiomRecognition True/On: "<</IdiomRecognition true>> setuserparams"
*?RIIdiomRecognition: "save
 currentuserparams dup /IdiomRecognition known
 {/IdiomRecognition get {(True)}{(False)} ifelse}
 {pop (None)}
 ifelse = flush
restore"
*End
*CloseUI: *RIIdiomRecognition

*% Halftone Information ===============
*DefaultHalftoneType: 1
*ScreenFreq: "71.0"
*ScreenAngle: "45.0"
*ResScreenFreq 400dpi: "65.0"
*ResScreenAngle 400dpi: "45.0"
*ResScreenFreq 600dpi: "71.0"
*ResScreenAngle 600dpi: "45.0"

*DefaultScreenProc: Dot
*ScreenProc Dot: "
 {abs exch abs 2 copy add 1 gt {1 sub dup mul exch 1 sub dup mul add 1 sub}
 {dup mul exch dup mul add 1 exch sub} ifelse}"
*End
*ScreenProc Line: "{pop}"
*ScreenProc Ellipse: "{dup 5 mul 8 div mul exch dup mul exch add sqrt 1
 exch sub}"
*End

*DefaultTransfer: Null
*Transfer Null: "{ }"
*Transfer Null.Inverse: "{1 exch sub}"

